Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在林檎轉學到田茂農之後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~　等一下　小老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　不用那麼急的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅總是那麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現也總是那麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們每到這時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像窮途末路一樣不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這　這是咋的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報警了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連圍欄也木有的啥都木有的田地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰　有目擊者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要線索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對　就是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿著灰色的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱著蔬菜跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那是在大概幾點左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天照顧完牛之後準備回去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概晚上8點多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候這個掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是事實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算怎麼辦　過真鳥繼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子的話　就必須嚴查事實和動機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫且不說是偷吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可如果是餓的不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特拉什　我累挺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　節子　花子　賣火柴的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福王子的燕子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上總是犧牲那些純潔弱小的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？中澤農
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正和過真鳥繼討論有可能阻礙社會發展的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個　不是猴子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　耕作　像猴子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是的　像猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等　那可是用兩腳走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野生的猴子也可以在短時間內用兩腳走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱著西瓜跑之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你　你有見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和農住的地方是偏遠農村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗和猴子還有山雞都會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本傳說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　太好啦　沒有不幸的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的　解散　解散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是　戰爭才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼第一次應對猿猴出現很頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對策考慮會議開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼一個人一個人的發表建議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的　那麼我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們老家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田地周圍都有通電柵欄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通電？辟里啪啦的那種？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不至於會死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快實行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為意見確實是沒什麼錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他吃的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是肚子餓了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他吃的肚子不餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會來破壞農田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　趕快實行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是個壞主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但問題是受襲擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是果樹啊田地而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明確的說有半分開玩笑的性質
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認為會因為肚子不餓了就老實了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼好像很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鄙人　畑耕作　16歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其大半的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都投入了和猿猴的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就是超級仁君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前仁君的30倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能一次發射30枚火箭煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很拽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓猴子們嘗嘗留下心理陰影級別的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火藥上潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　好孩子絕不要去瞄發射口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些俗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來告訴你們我的秘籍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼秘籍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了　你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿猴和人類都是靈長類動物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出誠意來對話的話一定能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶幸只有一支猿猴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它處理掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處理掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死它貌似不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,農業是無情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經做好了這個覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一個厲害的獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好　我叫大森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊？這個奇怪的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　說的太直接了　林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊這個奇怪的大叔是咋回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你這大胸都說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊過真鳥繼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有些許小期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找這個宅男樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人都是九分看外貌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一分是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就等著吃驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看大森先生這幅樣子可是吹箭的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹箭的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是大森流吹箭術的開山祖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來　吹箭在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是吹箭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是狙擊吹箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狙擊吹箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一看還以為是漫畫的海報什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來完全誤解了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不　這就是漫畫的海報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是把漫畫的海報捲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做成的吹箭筒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大森先生您平時用這吹箭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都狩獵什麼樣的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些現充吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉　原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個　抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大森先生你是做什麼工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被在下調製的強力麻藥射中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什麼猴子都會立馬　升天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商品名也是秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是將竹輪貼在嘴唇上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以命名為「乳頭式架勢」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個是被叫做現充殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死猴子　把你剝個精光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄了它弄了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這猴子　手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的　林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以同情他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是　首先是要保護田地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是因為受傷才脫離隊伍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是脫離隊伍後才受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是多餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是快點想想怎麼處理這傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良田　現在不是說笑的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是蠢　過真鳥繼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經考慮過這猴子的出路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和動物園工作的熟人商量過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問他是否願意接收這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此　動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　正好現在養的都是母猴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這只雄性放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為金龜婿也能促進那邊的氣氛活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的人生　不　新的猴生要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉　良田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記住你的恩惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說喵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記住恩惠喵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我　我才不是為了得到你的表揚喵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　是為了猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了　咋的啦　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有重要的事想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以等我一個小時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想盡早說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋　我有很多必須要準備的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎　耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你房間佈局換了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是的　你不要緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒　不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說　全部結束後一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　是繼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　我叫他來的　進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我進來　哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把室內佈局換了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白瞎了這麼可愛的YES圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕太　你有什麼事情要說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　嗯　是關於林檎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥啊　我還什麼都沒說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是去死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我活得好好的呢　話說　你抽什麼風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙　作死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼　作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之　你們來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友們　來　一起唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是草壁由佳的DVD吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都扔了那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你還藏著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是用零花錢重新買的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說　你們看由佳炭　沒注意到什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　雖然是廢話　人看起來很親切隨和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不會想到她和那個木下居然是同一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢　臉上一直是掛著笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個　笑容啊　笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那姑娘來到這以後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次都沒笑過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛進教室的時候　內褲事件的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯的時候　玩國王遊戲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和農比賽堅持到最後的時候　猴子得救的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎一直都是繃著臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為　這個笑容是職業微笑罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然如此　不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起生活的同伴一點都沒有笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會覺得寂寞麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起逗笑　缺少我的出場是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你在這裡　木下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說　你不想看看我的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒　好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,dark　matter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此　只能硬碰硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木下同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,農這傢伙　太讓人羨慕嫉妒恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過　幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呀　我的技術不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的看我的看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此　這招如何　是這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的「沈體」出賣了你　不用「面強」的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把一切交給「蒯感」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到極限了嗎　不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在　該我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你總是繃著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我以為你在這過得不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　你想逗我發笑是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起　我沒有惡意　那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡搞的分寸沒掌握好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我笑不出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始別人說我表情有點僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為是有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就沒想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　漸漸的　無論怎麼努力　都笑不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的表情也都擺不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然就不能在原來的地方再待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那個猴子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　那個猴子找到了自己的歸宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上真有笑不出來這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說不准　但是應該是精神上的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁由佳　木下林檎　是不是疲於應付
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍人的期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此　休息下會恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都不好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逗她笑　想逗她笑這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是我們的一廂情願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若旦那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是若旦那　我是蓋婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對　我是來向你傳達信息的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信　信息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來吧　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們人類　對我都做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在　你是在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘記　耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋婭我會一直向你耕作著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傾訴著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋婭　蓋婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類到底對蓋婭做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帶林檎去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓她看看那片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實　那片土地和現在的木下有相似之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那個　木下同學也會有所感悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在農校裡有農業俱樂部　也就是農俱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們現在要去的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從前輩那裡繼承的項目所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,項目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對　希望你也能加入進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不先看番茄地麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸那泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又硬又干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　那是死掉的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡種不了莊稼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是死掉了的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連作破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,補習的時候學過了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在同一個地方持續種植一種作物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會導致無法耕種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有些膚淺的人　通過使用化肥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算來避免產量下降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果導致病蟲害的擴散　農藥過度使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是愚蠢的惡性循環的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這土地不能恢復到原樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這塊田以前和剛才看到的土地是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是同一塊田地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩們在農俱中開始這個項目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們繼承下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能恢復到這個程度已經花了七年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然　還沒有完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　作物在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力地生長著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　這裡會重生是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耕作　我想嘗嘗那個番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒　現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想嘗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還沒熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:22:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎　你剛剛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木下同學　也嘗嘗這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個更紅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　木下同學　吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個已經很紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用心耕種的作物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以充盈人的身心　讓人感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,培育作物是最快樂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一天你也能體會到這份喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
